The ‘Island of Gods’ Bali, holds a lot of spiritual wisdom and traditional practices meant to bring balance to one’s life. I recently had the opportunity to experience a blessing ceremony in honor of a new venue we are opening. 

The purpose of a Bali blessing is to bring more harmony between yourself and the universe, balance the chakras, release karma from past lives that might still plague you, and encourage prime health, happiness, safety, finances, and a bright future for the you and the venue. 

The blessing includes a ceremony where holy water is poured on you for purification and the water is significant because it represent chi, or the flow of energy. The rice being placed on your forehead is for success and good fortune. 

#bali #indonesia #blessing #kuta

I’ve been fortunate to live in some amazing places - LA, Vegas, NC, NYC, and now Bali. It’s always a restart when you move, with new routines, new friends, and a whole new crew, especially when you don’t know anyone. Lately, I’ve been feeling super grateful for my Bali family. Can’t wait to make more memories together! Wish I could tag everyone 🏝️ #bali

Europe, how I have missed you! First stop: Amsterdam. Here are a few images from the start of the trip. From a random cyclone upon arrival to savoring great food and drinks, and never ending 11PM sunsets. Can’t wait to explore more. Next up: Athens & Mykonos. Hit me up with your absolute must-do’s / recommendations 🙏🏻

#amsterdam #europe #eurotrip

Second Stop: Madrid, Spain 🇪🇸 - a quick pit stop before hitting Ibiza. Full city tours, exploring massive 118-hectare palace gardens, plenty of sangria sipping, more endless sunsets, and discovering the streets early morning during 6K runs. Impromptu Bali fam meet ups and ending it all at @madcoolfestival, for an epic performance by @rufusdusol 

#madrid #spain #eurotrip #europe

Ibiza, Spain 🇪🇸 - So many amazing memories, plenty of new friends, and reuniting with old ones. A special shoutout to @leslee_tatman & @charliectatman. From club days/nights to Formentera boat trips, cliff jumping, random weddings, teepee conversations/dances, plenty of swimming, and endless eating. Until next time 🏝️

#Ibiza #Spain #EuroTrip

🏛️ Athens, Greece 🇬🇷 - There is always something magical about exploring cities with so much history. We embarked on our very own restaurant food tour, indulging in the most delicious Greek cuisine. Explored the Acropolis and the Parthenon while discovering many side streets filled with local music and vibrant energy. Living on an island, you sometimes miss out on these city vibes. Really enjoyed the limited time here before heading to Mykonos. 

#athens #greece #eurotrip

Mykonos, Greece 🇬🇷 - The grand finale of an unforgettable trip! Adventures with new and old friends, indulging in amazing food, more boat rides, and dancing to incredible music. Back in Bali now 🏝️ - until next time Europe. 

#mykonos #greece #eurotrip
